    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1554970/extras/b9ef32082004c3ac5e327e039d43dd32.avif?t=1713542210\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br>现实世界和灵界交织在一起，击败混沌大军，将米德拉王国从恶魔入侵者手中解救出来。<br><br>《Rogue Spirit》是一款带有轻度潜行元素的 3D rogue-lite 动作游戏。在游戏中扮演米德拉王国的幽灵王子，附身敌人并吸收其独特的技能，击退破坏王国故土的邪恶势力。<br><br><strong>游戏特色：</strong><br>• 带有潜行元素的独特Rogue-lite动作游戏<br>• 扮演坚定的米德拉王子“幽灵”<br>• 附身与你战斗的敌人，吸收其战斗特点，在战斗中全力以赴<br>• 精通不同角色的游戏风格，提升你的技能，适应这千变万化的世界<br>• 探索美妙的米德拉王国，学习其传说与学识<br>• 18 个拥有不同技能、武器和玩法的角色<br>• 体验在 5 个不同生物群落中随机生成的 10 个关卡<br>• 数十种道具和技能，每一次旅程都为玩家带来别样体验<br>• 每一次旅程均可解锁永久升级<br>• 世界奥秘和首领敌人等待着你来探索<br>• 受传统亚洲风格启发的 3D 画风<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1554970/extras/10006aa1c6c4d27cf68aa71b52c9a521.poster.avif?t=1713542210\" width=620 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1554970/extras/10006aa1c6c4d27cf68aa71b52c9a521.webm?t=1713542210\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1554970/extras/10006aa1c6c4d27cf68aa71b52c9a521.mp4?t=1713542210\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>扮演幽灵王子，探索米德拉王国。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1554970/extras/ea2a459c926752bbe323a7c54932580f.poster.avif?t=1713542210\" width=620 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1554970/extras/ea2a459c926752bbe323a7c54932580f.webm?t=1713542210\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1554970/extras/ea2a459c926752bbe323a7c54932580f.mp4?t=1713542210\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>附身敌人角色，吸收他们独特的力量，并根据